<s> Hello Tony, by rule == one of your httpd server's access control rules.  </s>
<s> Should be cleared if we change it to say "by your server".  </s>
<s> I don't know if you're authorized to write to the server, though.  </s>
<s> If it's so, there's a bug in the current release when editing a remote file.  </s>
<s> Amaya reports that the save failed, even though it succeded.  </s>
<s> To go around it, add to your thot.rc (or .thotrc  </s>
<s> file) the following line: NO_REREAD_CHECK=yes We already fixed this bug and it'll be out in a forthcoming minor release.  </s>
<s> Note that the syntax of the above rule will change to: DISABLE_PUT_CHECK (or some other nicer sounding name).  </s>
