<s> If you change the rule, please only use positive rules: Make it something like REREADCHECK or PUT_CHECK and not disable_.... or no_....!!!  </s>
<s> This avoids problems for peoples who don't read english verry well.  </s>
<s> Specially the no_... version is often misunderstood as the NumberOf_...... I would have the NO_REREAD_CHECK given a number value: 0 for none and 2 for twice!.  </s>
<s> So for this (new) rule: PUT_CHECK=true  </s>
<s> Corne Try not to let implementation details sneak into design documents.  </s>
